# 🔐 SECURE ENVIRONMENT SECRETS TEMPLATE
# =============================================================================
# 🚨 CRITICAL: This file contains templates for production secrets
# Copy this file and set actual values for production deployment
# NEVER commit actual secrets to version control
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# 🔐 PRODUCTION SECRETS - SET THESE BEFORE DEPLOYMENT
# =============================================================================

# 🚨 DATABASE CONFIGURATION
# Get from Supabase project settings
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.[PROJECT_REF]:[PASSWORD]@aws-0-[REGION].pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres

# 🚨 SUPABASE CONFIGURATION  
# Get from Supabase project settings -> API
SUPABASE_URL=https://[PROJECT_REF].supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=[YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY]
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=[YOUR_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY]

# 🚨 JWT SECRET - GENERATE STRONG SECRET
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 64
# Or use: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(64).toString('base64'))"
JWT_SECRET=[GENERATED_64_CHAR_SECRET]

# =============================================================================
# 📋 DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
# 
# ✅ DATABASE_URL: Set to your Supabase connection string
# ✅ SUPABASE_URL: Set to your Supabase project URL
# ✅ SUPABASE_ANON_KEY: Set from Supabase project settings
# ✅ SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY: Set from Supabase project settings
# ✅ JWT_SECRET: Generate and set strong 64-character secret
# 
# 🔧 DEPLOYMENT COMMANDS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp env.secrets.template .env.production.local
# 2. Edit: nano .env.production.local
# 3. Set all values above
# 4. Deploy with: docker-compose up --env-file .env.production.local
# 
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# 🛡️ SECURITY NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# 🔒 NEVER commit files containing actual secrets
# 🔒 Rotate secrets regularly (every 90 days)
# 🔒 Use different secrets for different environments
# 🔒 Store secrets in secure vault services (AWS Secrets Manager, etc.)
# 🔒 Monitor for secret exposure in logs and error messages
# 
# =============================================================================
